column5: What a beauty morning it was ......  ...gotta love turning the clocks back and hittin the water early again!!!!...  Was able to hook into a lil guy this morning along with 2 snot pike....the little snot rockets have become VERY aggressive hittin' 10'' and 14" baits  ..
Nice muskie  Great pics.......water looks pretty rough behind you  Thanx for sharing Streamerguy

WTG Steve, your on a roll now with the muskies on Sunday mornings !!  The little dink pike are the same up on Nippissing too when it comes to aggressivness and a 30" fish thinks nothing of trying to eat a 10" bait.
Nice job  Good incentive for my upcoming Tuesday trip to Gbay  TB
Nice little Muskie Steve was there any ice at the ramp this morning?  How did the Pontoon boat handle those huge waves
Very nice report, pics, and fish Steve!!!  ... and it does look like you're fixin' to be attacked by a herd of Tsunami's on the horizon!
